.TH LDTK 1 "June 2026" "ldtk 1.5.3" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
ldtk \- Level Designer Toolkit, a 2D level editor
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ldtk
.RI [ FILE .ldtk]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B LDtk
(Level Designer Toolkit) is a modern, free, open\-source 2D level editor for
game development. It works with tile layers, auto\-tiling rules, entities and
integer grids, and exports a clean JSON
.RB ( .ldtk )
project consumed by engines and frameworks such as LibGDX, Godot, Unity,
raylib and Heaps.
.PP
With no argument, LDtk opens its project chooser. Passing a
.I .ldtk
file opens that project directly.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I /opt/ldtk
The vendored upstream Electron application bundle.
.SH SEE ALSO
Project documentation at
.UR https://ldtk.io/docs/
.UE .
.SH AUTHORS
